	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>
	<p><strong>The Disclosed Entity Report is designed to give access to Disclosed Entity data for Health Care Providers.</strong></p>

	<p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>To generate a Disclosed Entity report, enter:</p>
        <br />
        <p>The Business Name, NPI Number and Address of the Provider.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>If the search is too broad, narrow it by entering the FEIN/TAXID and/or phone information.</p>
        <p><br />
        <p>Additionally up to 5 Associated Individuals can be searched for, as well as 5 Associated Businesses.</p>
        <p>Click on the relevant plus sign to add an additional Associated Individual/Business (up to 5 each).<br />
        <p><br />
        <p>For Associated Individuals, enter a minimum of First and Last Name, Address and either Date of Birth or SSN.<br />
        <p>For Associated Businesses, enter a minimum of Business Name, Address and FEIN.<br />
        <br /></p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>


